original: Lyberg, Einar Viktor, bankdirektör, Göteborg, f. 6/3/88 i Visby av hamn-kapt. J. E. L. o. Emelie Karlström. G. m. Vera Stenmark. Barnr Wolf f. 17, Hans 19, Anna Lisa 23. — Studrex. 07, Schartaus handrinst. i StMni 08. Anst. i A-B Gotlands Bank i Visby 09, tjg. v. Deutsche Bank Filiale i Hamburg 12-13, kassör i A-B Gotlands Bank i Visby 16, kanir. v. kont. i Sthlm 18, kontrchef v. A-B Karta & Oaxens Kalkbruk i Sthlm 18, kas-sadir. i Kopparbergs Ensk. Banks kont. i Sthlm o. Falun 19-22, verkst. dir. o. led. av styr. f. A-B Gbgs Banks kont. i Falun 22, dir. v. centrrkont. i Sthlm 35, v. verkst. dir. i Gbg sed. 41.
translated: Lyberg, Einar Viktor, bank director, Gothenburg, born on 6/3/88 in Visby to harbor captain J. E. L. and Emelie Karlström. Married to Vera Stenmark. Children: Wolf born in 17, Hans in 19, Anna Lisa in 23. — Completed studies at Studrex. in 07, Schartaus Handrinst. in StMni in 08. Employed at A-B Gotlands Bank in Visby in 09, worked at Deutsche Bank Filiale in Hamburg from 12-13, cashier at A-B Gotlands Bank in Visby in 16, junior accountant in Stockholm in 18, contract manager at A-B Karta & Oaxens Kalkbruk in Stockholm in 18, cash director at Kopparbergs Enskilda Bank's offices in Stockholm and Falun from 19-22, executive director and board member of A-B Gbgs Bank's offices in Falun in 22, director of central offices in Stockholm in 35, executive director in Gothenburg since 41.
